00:56:35,310 --> 00:56:38,910
I hate you, Do Min-joon.

834
00:56:38,910 --> 00:56:40,750
I even hate you more now.

835
00:56:40,750 --> 00:56:41,710
Please keep your distance.

836
00:56:41,710 --> 00:56:45,220
